      </textblock>
    </study_pop>
    <sampling_method>Non-Probability Sample</sampling_method>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Primary open angle glaucoma, with the diagnosis supported on structural and functional
             complementary exams according to the current European Glaucoma Society guidelines

          -  Healthy subjects from the General Ophthalmology Outpatient Clinic

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  age inferior to 18 years old

          -  primary closed angle glaucoma

          -  secondary open angle glaucoma

          -  previous intra-ocular surgery

          -  known or suspected corneal disease

          -  previous intra-ocular inflammation

          -  previous ocular trauma
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
